      <title>阿波罗全球第四季度利润超出预期，资产飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/apollo-globals-fourth-quarter-profit-tops-estimates-assets-surge-2025-02-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[得益于费用的强劲增长和退休业务的稳健表现，阿波罗全球管理公司第四季度利润超出预期，推动该公司股价在周二盘前交易中上涨 4%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/apollo-globals-fourth-quarter-profit-tops-estimates-assets-surge-2025-02-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 11:36:38 GMT</pubDate>
