      <title>法国巴黎银行的投资银行业务表现亮眼，提振股价</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bnp-paribas-beats-q4-forecast-trims-profit-target-year-ahead-2025-02-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国巴黎银行 (BNP Paribas) 公布季度盈利超出预期，得益于交易活动的激增，该银行在推进成本削减以提高盈利能力的举措下，股价也因此上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bnp-paribas-beats-q4-forecast-trims-profit-target-year-ahead-2025-02-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 06:15:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
